gobblin.data.management.version.finder

Class DatasetVersionFinder<T extends FileSystemDatasetVersion>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.version.finder.AbstractDatasetVersionFinder<T>
      • gobblin.data.management.version.finder.DatasetVersionFinder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of FileSystemDatasetVersion expected from this class.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    VersionFinder<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DatasetVersionFinder, GlobModTimeDatasetVersionFinder, UnixTimestampVersionFinder, WatermarkDatasetVersionFinder

    public abstract class DatasetVersionFinder<T extends FileSystemDatasetVersion>
extends AbstractDatasetVersionFinder<T>
implements VersionFinder<T>
    Class to find FileSystemDataset versions in the file system. Concrete subclasses should implement a (FileSystem, Properties) constructor to be instantiated. Provides a callback with just the path of the version getDatasetVersion(Path, Path). Use AbstractDatasetVersionFinder.getDatasetVersion(Path, FileStatus) if you need a callback with FileStatus of the version.
